  "text": "This study has several limitations. First, we investigated anti-HEV IgG seroprevalence in the adult population only. Data for children are scarce, and the risk factors remain to be thoroughly evaluated [CITATION_1] . Second, the sample issued from PGP was small in size with respect to the samples issued from blood donors and university. Third, we cannot exclude that other risk factors that seem to play a minor role in our study may be more prominent when increasing the sample size. Finally, the number of individuals included who were older than 70 years was small compared to other age groups, which may underestimate the overall seroprevalence calculated.",
